      <title>分析师称，Novo 的大规模交易导致丹麦克朗走弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/novo-s-massive-deal-drives-danish-krone-weakening-analysts-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据跟踪市场的分析师称，诺和诺德公司(Novo Nordisk A/S)主要所有者的一项价值165亿美元的交易引发了一些投资者抛售丹麦克朗，并导致丹麦克朗最近几天走软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/novo-s-massive-deal-drives-danish-krone-weakening-analysts-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 12:01:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
